        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "0d6MT",
          "name": "UEI Section",
          "width": 1737,
          "height": 1800,
          "fill": "$ea-white",
          "layout": "none",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "eqfDr",
              "x": 80,
              "y": 64,
              "name": "title",
              "fill": "$ea-magenta",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1577,
              "content": "Universal Earned Income",
              "textAlign": "center",
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu Mono",
              "fontSize": 36,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "vqUeX",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 120,
              "name": "subtitle",
              "fill": "$ea-dark-navy",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "Get Paid to Build Startup Communities",
              "textAlign": "center",
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu Mono",
              "fontSize": 24,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "N03OB",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 172,
              "name": "p1",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "In a future of hyper automation and AI, the most meaningful human effort will be what separates us from machines: our humanity and creativity.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "fvRZr",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 230,
              "name": "p2",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "That's why e-America is launching a new Universal Earned Income program that pays e-Americans to build startup communities. This is a new experiment. We're starting modestly, but we hope to grow the program as it gains traction.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "otedq",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 310,
              "name": "s1",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "1. Create an innovation-related event on Luma and add e-America as a host so it appears on the e-America global calendar. (Add as a host by adding e-America's email hello@e-america.org)",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Kxned",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 386,
              "name": "s2",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "2. Bring together five or more entrepreneurial-minded citizens in person for any real-world activity: coffee, walks, talks, sports, hiking, dancing, or anything you choose.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Zphh1",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 462,
              "name": "s3",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "3. Send us photos from the event or post them on social media and tag e-America.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "hpKm1",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 510,
              "name": "s4",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "4. Get paid 100 USDT for each event you host. (To start, we'll limit this to one event per person per month.)",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "E53vY",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 568,
              "name": "contact",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "Email uei@e-america.org to coordinate hosting or to ask any questions.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "oHvH4",
              "x": 369,
              "y": 618,
              "name": "quote",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 1000,
              "content": "The future of humanity is our humanity. Let's build startup communities. And get paid for it.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "textAlign": "center",
              "fontFamily": "Ubuntu",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal",
              "fontStyle": "italic"
            },
